flowchart TD
    A[Market Data] --> B[Harmonic Engine<br/>Generates base tone & modulation]
    B --> C{Phonics Router}
    D[Technical Indicators<br/>RSI, MACD, Volatility] --> E[Phonics Intelligence Layer<br/>Analyzes data for meaning]
    E --> C
    C --> F[Audio Output Mixer]
    
    C -.->|Command: “Warn user”| G
    subgraph G [Phonics Implementation]
        H[Text-to-Speech TTS<br/>e.g., “Warning: RSI overheating”]
        I[Symbolic Sound Alerts<br/>e.g., A sharp, quick chime]
        J[Prosody Engine<br/>Adjusts speech speed, pitch for urgency]
    end

    G --> F
    B --> F

    F --> K[Final Audio Output<br/>Harmonic soundscape + intelligent voiceovers]
